title: New Zealand mix popular Dec2005
description:
A compilation of New Zealand music I made for a friend in India back in 2005.  Features a range of popular sounds from over the years assembled to give a good flow.  This compilation clocks in at 81:45 minutes and can be burnt onto a CD (TDK ones work well) if you allow overburning (and remove 2 second track gaps).  Enjoy!
